    {
      "content": "Pricing and Billing when using Premium Storage",
      "pos": [
        25088,
        25134
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "When using Premium Storage, the following billing considerations apply:",
      "pos": [
        25135,
        25206
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Billing for a Premium Storage disk depends on the provisioned size of the disk.",
      "pos": [
        25210,
        25289
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure maps the disk size (rounded up) to the nearest Premium Storage Disk option as specified in the table given in the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Scalability and Performance Targets when using Premium Storage<ept id=\"p1\">](#scalability-and-performance-targets-when-using-premium-storage)</ept> section.",
      "pos": [
        25290,
        25548
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Billing for any provisioned disk is prorated hourly using the monthly price for the Premium Storage offer.",
      "pos": [
        25549,
        25655
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For example, if you provisioned a P10 disk and deleted it after 20 hours, you are billed for the P10 offering prorated to 20 hours.",
      "pos": [
        25656,
        25787
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "This is regardless of the amount of actual data written to the disk or the IOPS/throughput used.",
      "pos": [
        25788,
        25884
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Snapshots on Premium Storage are billed for the additional capacity used by the snapshots.",
      "pos": [
        25887,
        25977
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "For information on snapshots, see <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Creating a Snapshot of a Blob<ept id=\"p1\">](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/azure/hh488361.aspx)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        25978,
        26099
      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        26102,
        26261
      ],
      "content": "<bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Outbound data transfers<ept id=\"p1\">](http://azure.microsoft.com/pricing/details/data-transfers/)</ept> (data going out of Azure data centers) incur billing for bandwidth usage."
    },
    {
      "content": "For detailed information on pricing for Premium Storage,  DS-series VMs and GS-series VMs, see:",
      "pos": [
        26263,
        26358
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Storage Pricing",
      "pos": [
        26363,
